function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	local tEaters = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CMP_Step_TempleOfRot_Eaters")
	for i, idEater in pairs(tEaters) do
		Hydra.Wait(.3)
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idEater) then
			Hydra.ActorTriggerPhasedLoopingAnimationEnd(idEater)
			Hydra.QActorPower(idActor, "Generic_Taunt")
			Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idEater)
		end
	end
end

local function setupEncounter(idActorTrigger, idTarget)

	for i, idMob in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idActorTrigger)) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMob) then
			local idMarker = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idMob)[1]
			Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idMob, true)
			Hydra.ActorEnable(idMob)
			if Hydra.ActorGetSNOName(idMob) == S_ACTOR_TWOHAND then
				if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMarker) then
					Hydra.QActorPower(idMob, S_POWER_TWOHAND_LEAP_HEIGHT, idMarker)
					Hydra.QActorPower(idMob, S_POWER_TAUNT, idTarget)
				end
			elseif Hydra.ActorGetSNOName(idMob) == S_ACTOR_MELEE then
				Hydra.QActorPower(idMob, S_POWER_SUMMONED)
				Hydra.QActorPower(idMob, S_POWER_MELEE_WILDSWINGS, idTarget) 
			elseif Hydra.ActorGetSNOName(idMob) == S_ACTOR_DUALWIELD then
				Hydra.QActorPower(idMob, S_POWER_SUMMONED)
				Hydra.QActorPower(idMob, S_POWER_DUALWIELD_DASH, idTarget) 
			end			
			Hydra.Wait(0)
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMob) then
			Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idMob, false)
			Hydra.ActorSetAITether(idMob, idTarget)
			end
		end	
	end

end
